    public static final class LightningApi.LightningNode.Builder
extends com.google.protobuf.GeneratedMessageV3.Builder<LightningApi.LightningNode.Builder>
implements LightningApi.LightningNodeOrBuilder
    An individual vertex/node within the channel graph. A node is
connected to other nodes by one or more channel edges emanating from it. As the
graph is directed, a node will also have an incoming edge attached to it for
each outgoing edge.
    Protobuf type lnrpc.LightningNode
